g> Recommended.  Would probably choose a titanium spoon over the spork and insure it is of a size that it would fit in the pot.<\\/p><p>\\r\\n\\t<strong>Water Treatment - <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/gp\\/product\\/B000OR111G\\/ref=as_li_ss_tl?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">Aqua Mira<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"3\":\"pct\"}}', '2013-10-09 03:24:29', '2015-01-17 19:43:04', 'e0c23d1f-c41d-4f1c-9cc3-57e914270d61'),
