r any sort of guiding.  If you want to get really serious about wilderness first aid and have a free month, look at becoming a <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.nols.edu\\/wmi\\/courses\\/wemt.shtml\\\">Wilderness EMT<\\/a>.  I do not recommend taking a Wilderness First Aid course. Most of the friends who have taken one did not have a high retention of the material.<\\/p><h4>PCT First Aid Kit Supplies<\\/h4><p>One of the critiques that Amelia brought against my original PCT first aid kit was that I designed it not for myself but for everyone else.  This is a mindset that I gradually moved away from in the first few weeks. My final first aid kit was designed solely for thru-hikers.<\\/p><ul><li>Tweezers<\\/li><li>Safety pins<\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Mehaz-Eyebrow-Mustach-Scissors-371\\/dp\\/B000IQ2ZYK\\/ref=sr_1_3?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">Mini-Scissors<\\/a><\\/li><li>Ace bandage<\\/li><li>Ibuprofen<\\/li><li>Benadryl<\\/li><li>Loperamide<\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Neosporin-Relief-Maximum-Strength-Antibiotic\\/dp\\/B000052XQ4?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">Neosporin<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Neosporin-Relief-Maximum-Strength-Antibiotic\\/dp\\/B000052XQ4?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.macssmack.com\\/?product=ultimate-fix\\\">Mac Smack\'s Ultimate Fix<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.macssmack.com\\/?product=ultimate-fix\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/gp\\/product\\/B0009RFB3U\\/ref=oh_details_o06_s01_i02?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">Johnson & Johnson Sports Tape<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/gp\\/product\\/B0009RFB3U\\/ref=oh_details_o06_s01_i02?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\"><\\/a>Moleskin<\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/2nd-Skin-Blister-Pad-CS6\\/dp\\/B0002DL784\\/ref=sr_1_3?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">2nd Skin Blister Pads<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Dr-Scholls-Cushions-6-Count-Packages