 ('192', '129', '1', '1', 'en_us', '8', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Gear Review - Clothing\",\"slug\":\"gear-review-clothing\",\"postDate\":1382857200,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\t<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.pcta.org\\/discover-the-trail\\/\\\">According to the PCTA,<\\/a> the Pacific Crest Trail travels through three national monuments, five state parks, seven national parks, 24 national forests and 47 wilderness areas.  It traverses deserts, forests, mountains, and snow. You reach an elevation of 13,153 feet at Forester Pass and go nearly to sea level at Cascade Locks. Temperatures on the trip will range from 0\\u00b0-110\\u00b0 Fahrenheit and include everything from scalding heat to downpours to a couple feet of snow.  And, lest we forget, swarms of mosquitos and wind storms make regular appearances.<\\/p><p>\\r\\n\\tOne\'s clothing is, thus, incredibly important.  Here\'s what I had for the duration of the trail.<\\/p><h4>Daily<\\/h4><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Hiking Shirt: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.railriders.com\\/men-eco-mesh-shirt-p-963.html?cPath=90_96\\\">RailRiders Eco-Mesh Shirt<\\/a><\\/li>\\t<li>Hiking Pants: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.railriders.com\\/men-bone-flats-pants-p-992.html?cPath=104_110\\\">RailRiders Bone Flats Pants<\\/a><\\/li>\\t<li>Underwear: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/gp\\/product\\/B001M0MMVC\\/ref=as_li_ss_tl?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">ExOfficio Give-N-Go Boxer<\\/a><\\/li>\\t<li>Hat: Straw Hat from KMart<\\/li>\\t<li>Socks: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Darn-Tough-Merino-Micro-Cushion\\/dp\\/B000XFW6OU\\/ref=sr_1_1?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">Darn Tough<\\/a><\\/li>\\t<li>Mosquito Head Net: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/gp\\/product\\/B001CTVNV8\\/ref=as_li_ss_tl?tag=reedmaniaccom-20\\\">Sea to Summit Mosquito Head Net<\\/a><\\/li>\\t<li>Gaiters: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.dirtygirlgaiters.com\\/goingbatty.html\\\">Dirty Girl Gaiters - Going Batty<\\/a><\\/li>\\t<li>S