 ('229', '135', '1', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"A Terrible Inconvenience\",\"slug\":\"a-terrible-inconvenience\",\"postDate\":1398573000,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Content goes here.<\\/p>\",\"3\":\"personal\"}}', '2014-04-27 03:13:02', '2015-01-17 19:43:04', '880211de-f023-4dff-a58f-3d0fe754dcd7'),
 ('230', '135', '1', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"A Terrible Inconvenience\",\"slug\":\"a-terrible-inconvenience\",\"postDate\":1398573000,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>In the continuing saga of navel gazing because, let us be honest, YouTube is growing a bit stale, we evaluate why I prefer to spend my time on a Saturday night working or writing blog entries instead of heading out for \\\"fun\\\". Self-indulgent,&nbsp;magniloquent,&nbsp;florid prose will undoubtedly make brief appearances in an attempt to&nbsp;disguise any semblance of well-thought out rhetoric. &nbsp;Extra-hyphens and random semicolons may; or may not; help provide humorous interludes from any and all seriousness. &nbsp;Seems like an appropriate time for a second paragraph.<\\/p><p>When did drinking alcohol become the&nbsp;irrepressible&nbsp;mainstay of adult fun? Please, do not get me wrong: I <em>like<\\/em> alcohol. The sheer scope of varieties and concoctions are a testament to our species love of it.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"3\":\"personal\"}}', '2014-04-27 03:27:58', '2015-01-17 19:43:04', 'f06b4fac-e3de-481c-bab7-58b32fcb8685'),
