ects. &nbsp;I do not mind hanging out and having a drink. The drink aspect is not normally appealing to me, but I am willing to make that sacrifice to be social, with select people. But, a party where you know most participants will be quite drunk by the end is both unenjoyable and boring. &nbsp;More and more I will skip such an event and spend the night watching a movie or reading a book at home, alone.<\\/p>\",\"3\":\"personal\"}}', '2014-04-27 05:20:49', '2015-01-17 19:43:04', '58d9568c-0b67-4f14-a5b3-9de8d70bbf43'),
