he day.  I grabbed my book and made the most of the day by simply lounging around town.  My tendency to go full bore meant I had not taken a single day off for the entire trip just to relax and enjoy the scenery.  Remedied that.  Saw quite a bit of wildlife too, including two <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.flickr.com\\/photos\\/133323973@N07\\/20868579641\\/in\\/album-72157657725794351\\/\\\">sea lions having dinner<\\/a> in the marina.\\r\\n<\\/p><p>That night I reviewed my credit card balance and decided that after an intense two week whirlwind through SE Alaska that it was time to head back south and start thinking about finding employment once more.  A truly amazing trip, highly recommended.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}', '2015-09-20 23:11:52', '2015-09-20 23:11:52', '9e68f9b1-c20e-4f38-bc7f-86abd4bd9b81'),
