 ('452', '191', '1', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Syrian Refugee Debate: A Closer Look - Late Night with Seth Meyers\",\"slug\":\"the-syrian-refugee-debate-a-closer-look-late-night-with-seth-meyers\",\"postDate\":1448040544,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=VmpZcvvyML8\\\">Link<\\/a>.  Half of the state governors and pretty much every GOP Presidential candidate wants to either block or greatly restrict the number of Syrian Refugees entering the United States. Seth Meyers provides a nice introduction into why this is just stupid.  Amazing how the GOP seems to be the least \\\"Christian\\\" of the two parties.<\\/p>\"}}', '2015-11-20 17:29:04', '2015-11-20 17:29:04', '8313872b-ed79-41f7-9732-2fe610fd3a2f');
