 ('31', 'field', '1', 'en_us', ' coder wilderness emt geek vagabond lover of knowledge pursuer of fun thru hiked the pacific crest trail in 2013 trail name blur mark well as heaven and earth are fairer fairer far than chaos and blank darkness though once chiefs and as we show beyond that heaven and earth in form and shape compact and beautiful in will in action free companionship and thousand other signs of purer life so on our heels a fresh perfection treads a power more strong in beauty born of us and fated to excel us as we pass in glory that old darkness nor are we thereby more conquer d than by us the rule of shapeless chaos keats the human word is neither immortal nor invulnerable but it is the power that orders our chaos and the light by which we live northrop frye '),
